quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Have you seen the one who denies that there is a just divine system in place for mankind
  107,2,Such a one it is that pushes the orphan away
  107,3,And does not motivate others on feeding the poor
  107,4,"And, woe to those who pray —"
  107,5,"Those who are neglectful of, and/or inattentive in, their Prayers"
  107,6,Those who show off
  107,7,And refuse to give even trifling things to others